## JavaScript Animation Functions

<augment_code_snippet path="01-CSS-Wizard-Foundation/building-website-from-scratch/script.js" mode="EXCERPT">
```javascript
function hideCard(card) {
 // Animate out
 card.animate([
 { opacity: 1, transform: 'scale(1)' },
 { opacity: 0, transform: 'scale(0.9)' }
 ], {
 duration: 300,
 easing: 'ease-in',
 fill: 'forwards'
 }).addEventListener('finish', () => {
