 378	 <h3 class="card__title">What do I need to start mushroom foraging?</h3>
 379	 <p>You'll need a local field guide, a sharp knife or scissors, a basket or mesh bag for collecting, and paper bags for separating specimens. Bring a small brush for cleaning, wear sturdy boots, and carry a GPS device or compass to track your location. A camera is also helpful to document your finds.</p>
